These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, peasade
There 2 different types of food: plum, peas
1. the person drinking peasade is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the person drinking peasade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | peasade  | almond-milk |
| Food       | plum | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | mirinda |
| Sport      | soccer     | basketball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, crime
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, german
1. the indonesian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | crime  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
