There 2 different types of food: garlic, apple
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk   |
| Food       | apple | garlic |

