.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, canadian
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog
1. the canadian is on the left or right of the russian##3
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | russian | canadian |
| Pet           | frog     | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, traveling
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, project-manager
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | traveling | rock-climbing |
| Job     | coach        | project-manager |

